{"tid":2079943,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【軍事台】震驚！臺灣國防企業已掌握製造氮化鎵(GaN) AESA雷達的技術","createTime":"2020-06-26T06:14:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T08:19:10.000Z","uid":120678,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eeec22023acd039a8669a4dfe98e7e82e17f8aec","tid":2079943,"uid":120678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:14:17.000Z","msg":"source：<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.yahoo.com/taiwan-aesa-radar-challenge-international-080000526.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.yahoo.com%2Ftaiwan-aesa-radar-challenge-international-080000526.html&d=b6PV2mHT5tDC6%2Fq4CXK2SkpSq8GU1PbbWBdRLYKbGpc%3D&h=c9d226c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.yahoo.com/taiwan-aesa-radar-challenge-international-080000526.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.hpcismart.com/images/website/ManChemNews/DIR_120/F_77248.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hpcismart.com%2Fimages%2Fwebsite%2FManChemNews%2FDIR_120%2FF_77248.jpg&h=99731e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n顯微鏡下的氮化鎵結晶<br />\n<br />\n氮化鎵(GaN) AESA雷達係目前雷達同電子作戰技術既Gold Standard<br />\n比起傳統砷化鎵(GaAs)半導體零件有壓倒性既優勢<br />\n響以前，氮化鎵雷達技術只有日本、美國、歐洲掌握<br />\n日本秋月級FCS-3A係最早用氮化鎵既AESA雷達<br />\n目前美國已進入量產階段既SPY-7同SPY-6雷達都係用氮化鎵<br />\n另外歐洲瑞典既愛立信公司亦成功開發出Erieye氮化鎵雷達，並安裝響「全球眼」預警機上<br />\n以色列2015年建成的國防戰略級早期預警雷達EL/M-2090亦都係用氮化鎵<br />\n臺灣開發出氮化鎵雷達的技術，代表臺灣已進入全球只有極少數國家掌握既GaN雷達俱樂部<br />\n亦都代表臺灣響高精密電子零件、先進材料科學技術上遙遙領先中共<br />\n根據報導原來呢又係關小英事，係小英推動臺灣「國防自主」戰略既其中一個成果"},{"pid":"140f16ba0e7a588e7f80face08634c92e90d5dcb","tid":2079943,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T06:32:49.000Z","msg":"台灣識即係支共要偷又易左.<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ec4941c4699c56c2a9d969bb0b95c2c66d2a99","tid":2079943,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":